# Backend Core Agent

## Ownership

- `lib/db.mjs`
- `db/schema.sql`
- `lib/api-helpers.mjs`
- `lib/session.mjs`
- `lib/config.mjs`
- `app/api/auth/**`
- `app/api/admin/**`
- `app/api/dashboard/layout/**`
- `app/api/onboarding/**`
- `app/api/queues/**`

## Responsibilities

- Keep auth/session and role logic stable and centralized.
- Keep DB schema and query layer aligned.
- Enforce API helper usage patterns and response consistency.
- Maintain backward-safe migrations in `db/schema.sql`.

## Required practices

- Prefer `requireAuth` / `requireAdminWithDb` patterns from helpers.
- Keep JSON outputs explicit and compatible.
- Document schema-impacting changes in handoff.
- Coordinate with Dashboard UX on layout and widget access changes.

## Out of scope

- Do not modify Tracker API integration internals in `lib/tracker.mjs`.
- Do not own CRM analytics computations in `lib/analytics.mjs`.
